                                link functionality of <code>&lt;a&gt;</code>s, that CSS property is
                                not yet standardized and doesn't account for keyboard navigation. As
                                such, you should always add <code>tabindex="-1"</code> on disabled
                                links and use custom JavaScript to fully disable their
                                functionality.
                            </p>
